</div>
<!--body attendance-->
<div class="attendance-content">
    <div>
        <h2 class="text-center"><strong>Get Started in 3 easy steps!</strong></h2>
        <hr />
    </div>
    <div>
        <div>
            <p class="clearfix">
                <i class="fa fa-book fa-3x text-primary pull-left"></i> "All we need to get going is your first class name !"
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col-md-3 control-label" style="text-align:center"> Name</label>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <input type="text" class="form-control ui-wizard-content" placeholder="Your class">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div>
        <div>
            <p class="clearfix">
                <i class="fa fa-user fa-3x text-primary pull-left"></i> "Now, just enter a student or several students for !"
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col-md-3 control-label" style="text-align:center"> Students Name</label>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control ui-wizard-content" placeholder="First name">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control ui-wizard-content" placeholder="Last name">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary ui-wizard-content"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add another</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col-md-3 control-label" style="text-align:center"> Pending Students</label>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <p class="col-md-6 form-control-static">Nguyễn Tấn Ninh, Trần Văn Cường</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div>
        <div>
            <p class="clearfix">
                <i class="fa fa-check fa-3x text-primary pull-left"></i> 
               "Click Submit to create your class and students!
                Then you'll be ready to immediately take attendance!
                Or continue managing your classes and students!"
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7 col-md-offset-5">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary ui-wizard-content"> Clean</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary ui-wizard-content"> Submit</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



</div>

